file_content.text: Halt! Leave Cortess lands immediately or be forcibly expelled.
What are you talking about?
What?
You'd speak this way to the baron's guest?
This is improper!
Let me guess--Baroness Chay doesn't like me anymore.
I shouldn't be surprised.
The baroness has revoked your access to the estate. She's ordered all defenses raised.
You may as well turn around. We've got blast doors, force fields--this estate is designed to repel an army.
All right--I'm leaving, Captain.
I'll go.
Then you'll forgive me if I make absolutely certain.
The baroness is funding terrorists, and I have proof!
Chay is a criminal.
I'm not interested in your "proof." I'm interested in removing a threat to my house.
An army? Maybe I'll have to break a sweat.
That'll make this interesting.
You want to play it that way, that's how we'll play it.
All droids--attack now!
Fun. Don't think blasters are going to get us through here, agent--maybe we should talk to your Bugboy.
